The KeyXentic KX906 Smart Token is a USB security token provides functions like identification, authorization, fingerprint authentication and etc.

About KeyXentic Native Messaging:
- Communicate with KeyXentic KX906 Smart Token
- Provide APIs for developers to use the functionalities of the KeyXentic KX906 Smart Token such as asymmetric key generation, signature and verification.
- Serve as an example for developers to quickly test and build up applications on top of the KeyXentic Native Messaging extension.

About KeyXentic KX906 Smart Token:
- Data security and personal privacy should be in an intuitive and convenient way without compromise. KeyXentic Inc. provides a secure one stop shop for your daily life. Platform free, multi-modal bio-authenticated and certified secure key is what you need.
- For more info, please visit our website: https://www.keyxentic.com/kx906
